.php?tid=32043607&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=165225673568d6f6f681e179_30870508"/><published>2025-09-27T03:44:30+08:00</published></entry></feed>